OL,3,C'I just had to suffer' - Disabled
OL,4,Cwoman forced to 'crawl' along theme
OL,5,Cpark queue
OL,7,FA disabled woman from Rhondda Cynon
OL,8,FTaf says her visit to the UK's biggest
OL,9,Ftheme park was "ruined" because she
OL,10,Fwasn't issued with accessible tickets
OL,11,Ffor the rides.
OL,13,FHeather Giles has Early Onset
OL,14,FParkinsons disease and pre-booked the
OL,15,Fpasses to Alton Towers but was told on
OL,16,Fthe day there were none left.
OL,18,FShe says she had to spend hours in
OL,19,Flong queues which caused pain and
OL,20,Fforced her to cut the family day out
OL,21,Fshort.
