OL,5,Cpark queue
OL,7,FBosses at the park say they are
OL,8,Fdedicated to fostering inclusive
OL,9,Fexperiences for all guests.
OL,11,F"Myself and my friend Anthony - who
OL,12,Fhas epilepsy - and his family spent
OL,13,Fthree hours queuing and I was in so
OL,14,Fmuch pain", Heather explained.
OL,16,F"I just sat on the floor in the queue
OL,17,Fline and just crawled along the queue
OL,18,Fline.
