OL,3,C'I just had to suffer' - Disabled
OL,4,Cwoman forced to 'crawl' along theme
OL,5,Cpark queue
OL,7,F"We told them (staff at the theme
OL,8,Fpark) I've got Parkinsons I can't
OL,9,Fstand in the queue and they said there
OL,10,Fwas nothing they could do to hemp me."
OL,12,FShe continued: "It was pretty
OL,13,Fhumiliating to be honest. I was really
OL,14,Ffrustrated, I've been before and it
OL,15,Fwas really good the way the access
OL,16,Fpasses worked and it just feels like
OL,17,Fthey just don't care.
OL,19,F"I just had to suffer and Im still
OL,20,Fsuffering now because of it."
