OL,5,Cpark queue
OL,7,FAnthony Bartley has a brain tumour
OL,8,Fwhich causes severe epilepsy and can
OL,9,Fhave 20-30 seizures a day.
OL,11,FHe says The stress of queuing for
OL,12,Fhours and not being assisted by stuff
OL,13,Fmembers trigged his condition and made
OL,14,Fit a painful experience.
OL,16,F"I think they've taken for granted the
OL,17,Ffact that a little card actually saves
OL,18,Ffor me a lot of distress", he said.
