OL,7,F"And for my family a lot of distress
OL,8,Fbecause my wife has to pick me up if I
OL,9,Ffall on the floor and my kids have to
OL,10,Fstand with me if I fall on the floor.
OL,12,F"I believe their way of handling
OL,13,Fqueues to potentially be quite
OL,14,Fdangerous."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Merlin
OL,17,FEntertainments, who own Alton Towers,
OL,18,Fsaid: "we're saddened to learn that
OL,19,FHeather and Anthony feel their
OL,20,Fexperience did not meet their
OL,21,Fexpectations.
