OL,7,F"In March, we introduced a pre-booking
OL,8,Fportal to minimise wait times for
OL,9,Fthose who require additional support.
OL,11,F"On the day of visit, if a guest still
OL,12,Fhas not pre-booked a Ride Access Pass
OL,13,F, they can speak to a member of our
OL,14,Fteam who then release these to other
OL,15,Fguests on a first-come first serve
OL,16,Fbasis."
