OL,7,FA spokesperson for Disability Wales
OL,8,Fsaid: "Theme parks pose significant
OL,9,Fchallenges for disabled individuals,
OL,10,Foften turning what should be an
OL,11,Fenjoyable experience into a deeply
OL,12,Fstressful one.
OL,14,F"The extensive queuing systems,
OL,15,Fdesigned without consideration for
OL,16,Fdiverse needs, can cause unbearable
OL,17,Fphysical pain and immense
OL,18,Fpsychological distress.
