OL,7,F"Without such provisions, disabled
OL,8,Fpeople are often excluded from
OL,9,Fenjoying time with family and friends,
OL,10,Freinforcing their isolation.
OL,12,F"Yet, even when these accommodations
OL,13,Fare available, disabled individuals
OL,14,Fface harsh judgment and skepticism
OL,15,Ffrom others who question their
OL,16,Fentitlement, particularly when their
OL,17,Fimpairments are invisible.
